data.description: This charming 3 bedroom 2 bathroom home on a spacious corner lot is located in the heart of historical Bartow. The property is conveniently located minutes away from all the major shopping centers as well as Lakeland, Winter Haven and Mulberry. The home features a spacious   26 x 15 primary bedroom with a private exterior entrance, split bedroom floor plan, ceramic tiles, walk in closets, solid wood cabinets and a anchored large 10 x 20 shed with electricity. Don't hesitate and schedule your showing today. Owner is motivated to sell.
